Name: Frequency of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ occurring after \First Look-Your updates are overdue\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' for cases where activity 'First Look-Your updates are overdue' occurs

Name: Percentage of manuscripts that reach \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ without \SW-Reviewer Agreed\
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all cases where 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' does not happen

Name: Number of times \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ is the final activity before \Manuscript Export Succeeded\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' for cases where activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' occurs

Name: Percentage of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ followed by \Manuscript Export Succeeded\ out of all occurrences of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Frequency of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ in relation to the total number of activities in the event log
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Number of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ occurrences preceded by \First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' for cases where activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' occurs

Name: Percentage of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ that lead to a \SW-EIC Accept\ decision
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Frequency of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ as a precursor to \Manuscript Export Succeeded\ compared to \SW-Reviewer Agreed\ leading to \Manuscript Export Succeeded\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' for cases where activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' occurs

Name: Percentage of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ in manuscripts that eventually get accepted (followed by \SW-EIC Accept\) compared to those that do not
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Number of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ occurrences grouped by month
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'total', 'group_by': 'month'}

Name: Percentage of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ followed by any activity related to manuscript acceptance or revision
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Frequency of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ in manuscripts with more than one \SW-Reviewer Agreed\
Metric: the sum of the function base > 1 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Percentage of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ in the total number of activities for manuscripts that require major revision (\SW-EIC Major Revision\)
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'SW-EIC Major Revision'

Name: Number of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ occurrences that are followed by \First Look-Please submit updates\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' for cases where activity 'First Look-Please submit updates' occurs

Name: Percentage of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ occurrences that lead to a change in manuscript status (e.g., accepted, revised, rejected)
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'SW-EIC Accept'
